stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> AccountRecovery
    AccountRecovery --> VerifyIdentity: Start Recovery
    VerifyIdentity --> IdentityVerified: Identity Verified
    VerifyIdentity --> IdentityFailed: Identity Verification Failed
    IdentityVerified --> SelectRecoveryMethod: Choose Recovery Method
    SelectRecoveryMethod --> RecoveryViaEmail: Email Recovery
    SelectRecoveryMethod --> RecoveryViaSMS: SMS Recovery
    RecoveryViaEmail --> EmailSent: Recovery Email Sent
    RecoveryViaSMS --> SMSSent: Recovery SMS Sent
    EmailSent --> ResetPassword: Reset Password
    SMSSent --> ResetPassword: Reset Password
    ResetPassword --> [*]: Password Reset Complete
    IdentityFailed --> [*]: Recovery Failed

    [*] --> NumberChange
    NumberChange --> VerifyIdentityForNumberChange: Verify Identity
    VerifyIdentityForNumberChange --> IdentityVerifiedForNumberChange: Identity Verified
    VerifyIdentityForNumberChange --> IdentityFailedForNumberChange: Identity Verification Failed
    IdentityVerifiedForNumberChange --> EnterNewNumber: Enter New Phone Number
    EnterNewNumber --> ConfirmNewNumber: Confirm New Phone Number
    ConfirmNewNumber --> NumberChanged: Phone Number Changed
    NumberChanged --> [*]: Change Complete
    IdentityFailedForNumberChange --> [*]: Number Change Failed